settings.description: the end of the line is now here. one final half of Bowser's newest castle awaits, and it's filled to the brim with bros! think you can take down the king in this dangerous trek?
Pulley Platforms react to the Mario Bros.'s weight. Always keep an eye on both platforms at the same time and make sure you have the room you need to jump!
#8993-090 = Jump from block to block in order to escape the unexpectedly deadly opera center.

Not a Rip-off of an existing series called "The 8 Worlds" I swear. This is the Desert Airship, and transition to water land.
